tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE cloud_cover_data (
    date TIMESTAMP PRIMARY KEY,
    cloud_cover FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE weather_forecasts (
    forecast_date TIMESTAMP PRIMARY KEY,
    temperature FLOAT,
    wind_speed FLOAT,
    is_raining BOOL
)

CREATE TABLE CloudCoverData (
    date DATE,
    time TIME,
    cloud_coverage FLOAT,
    location VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE WeatherForecasts (
    date DATE,
    forecast VARCHAR,
    temperature FLOAT,
    precipitation FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE UserFeedback (
    user_id INT,
    feedback TEXT,
    rating INT
)

CREATE TABLE ForecastAccuracy (
    date DATE,
    actual_weather VARCHAR,
    forecasted_weather VARCHAR,
    accuracy_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE weather_forecasts (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    location VARCHAR(50),
    predicted_cloud_cover FLOAT,
    actual_cloud_cover FLOAT
);
